{"type": "article", "id": 31190, "title": "你还记得自己买的第一盒磁带吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-18T23:14:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31675, "name": "Outofstock"}, {"id": 31676, "name": "Bolia"}, {"id": 31677, "name": "Line Studio"}, {"id": 31678, "name": "Pedro Paulo Venzon"}, {"id": 31679, "name": "Katie Ford"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160819092315ExbSh6nZr0tjzQi9.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Cassette Table by TAYBLES</h3><p>你还记得自己买的第一盒磁带吗？它现在去哪儿了？洛杉矶 TAYBLES 工作室推出的这些 Cassette Table 咖啡桌或许会勾起你的回忆，并且将创意与实用性很好地结合起来。每一款的桌面都忠实地还原了磁带的造型：转轮被改造为可以放杯子的凹洞，观察正前方采用磁性开阖的柜门你甚至还能发现一条木制“磁带”，打开后是一个可以收纳遥控器和其他杂物的空间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/214Graffiti\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价从 1599 到 2299 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002629HcfC8U9hOaiTLdWY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002630yqIVGZTP2dbLeONH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002630xNjDSlTbfgaIckMV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.632667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002630KbMTNifl5U39WZvF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002628DQG1gX4extkL7Cpl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.624667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Slow Dance by Slow Dance team</h3><p>生活节奏越来越快，那种因为发现某个奇妙的自然变化而感到欣喜的时刻似乎已经很久没有发生过了。最近一支来自美国的设计团队推出了一款根据视觉暂留原理而设计的画框 Slow Dance，希望借此提醒人们不要忽略发生在周围的美好细节：用画框内的夹子固定住一根羽毛或是一朵花，它就会根据不同模式缓缓地摇曳起来。这种慢镜头的效果是由每秒闪烁 80 次的灯光与高速震动的物体同步而形成的，像是在空白的“画布”上进行一次特别的“创作”。当你凝视这幅融合了科技与艺术的“画作”时，会有一种平静的感觉。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/xercyn/slow-dance-a-frame-that-slows-down-time\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 249 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002722V85Lqj6uRiIsZOlX.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608190027237VTO4nahM1UrZcmt.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002726s32145FDb6rALURN.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002725mlkvzJ6Kt8wBdFch.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002726aHZfkivYeBJpoNIW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002728QyzCpgBmrKI7Xcs3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Stamp by Outofstock</h3><p>设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.outofstockdesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Outofstock</a> 最近与丹麦家具品牌 Bolia 联手打造了由一软一硬两种材质构成的几何形吊灯 Stamp。为了同时呈现出两种几何形状，坚硬的吹制玻璃前后各包覆了一块柔软的热压工业毛毡。这个看似简单的设计实际上有着奇特的视觉效果：当你站在不同的角度进行观察，所看到的灯具形状也会发生变化，模糊了平面与立体之间的边界。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.bolia.com/en/products/20-104-01_24\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 199 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002800ke5y0iC79poMEJvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002800ipgwdfWvcsTkQZI1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002800ZNkfvWCu3nidTr0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002800TyOuEQ4gCHXDzS3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002800CIF0TWXQlrpybOfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713867\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pudica Chair by Pedro Paulo Venzon</h3><p>这款名为 <a href=\"http://pedrovenzon.com/Pudica\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pudica</a> 的椅子是巴西设计师 <a href=\"http://pedrovenzon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pedro Paulo Venzon</a> 的最新作品，延续了他极简而精致的设计风格。椅子由一个自成一体的的金属框架和两片作为椅背和座位的几何形金属板构成，纤细优雅的结构带给人一种赏心悦目的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002831JIzh8cgCRbEu3HQP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002831Z6XaAi7MtIVnpTdh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002831SUiVr9mogAcZdlPM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002833ebI8nvNDJGqiLZXS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002831hpzO2XZdLGQT14lE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002831B2HXYQ5sCEcFNehr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>KLIPP by Line Studio</h3><p>没有钟面的挂钟已经不算什么稀奇的创意了，这款由基辅 <a href=\"http://linestudio.com.ua/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Line Studio</a> 的建筑师 Max Voytenko 所设计的 <a href=\"http://linestudio.com.ua/gallery/klipp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">KLIPP</a> 挂钟采用了一种更简洁的方式来呈现时间。除了抛弃钟面之外，Voytenko 对指针也进行了改造，弯曲的金属框架看起来就像是被分开的回形针一样，石英机芯则被收纳在中间的圆盒内。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002907bumz93YgnHrCN8w0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608190029081b9v0XfIQcuAV6nJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002909rxbzvVfGoKO358mu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002909A0lRo6PGgcF1ZqNd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016081900291048o52ij0bWUKThs9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819002913OyxQvAUdMY36PN7i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sarah Duvous by Katie Ford</h3><p>这套为概念肥皂品牌 Sarah Duvous 所打造的包装是澳大利亚设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/katieforddesign\" rel=\"nofollow\">Katie Ford</a> 的作品。为了强调品牌的法国血统以及原材料中的植物元素，Ford 用丙烯酸颜料绘制出墨迹般的抽象画作为外包装，呈现出一种独特的田园风情。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819003018k51Phz98fT4CKern.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.924071\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819003017bDVXgFW82RMLES3o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795732\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819003018V6DOKz2EvT4rnuoq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.912308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608190030176YhGnbvIgDdVeyEt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819003017zIhSpc9VFy0B2J51.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.821138\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160819003018XhqVYNJr0e2zt4lG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709887\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}